Package com.ibm.mobile.applaunch.android.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AppLaunchListener
    This is the callback for AppLaunch SDK APIs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AppLaunch
    A singleton that serves as an entry point to IBM Cloud AppLaunch service communication.
    AppLaunchConfig
    AppLaunchConfig contains configuration of AppLaunch Service which is used by AppLaunch APIs.
    AppLaunchConfig.Builder
    Builder class of AppLaunchConfig.
    AppLaunchFailResponse
    This is the Failure Response class in the AppLaunch.
    AppLaunchResponse
    This is the Success Response class in the AppLaunch.
    AppLaunchUser
    AppLaunchUser contains user information which is used by AppLaunch APIs.
    AppLaunchUser.Builder
    Builder class of AppLaunchUser.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ErrorCode
    ErrorCode is an enumerator which contains error information.
    ICRegion
    ICRegion is an enumerator which can be used to specify IBM Cloud region where AppLaunch Service is hosted.
    RefreshPolicy
    RefreshPolicy is an enumerator which can be used to specify on how frequently the engagements should be fetched from the server.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AppLaunchException
    This is the exception which can be thrown by AppLaunch APIs.
